name: Structure_Bocca_4-shelf_Wide_Bookcase
reviews: Made in Denmark, eco friendly. Great construction- really solid piece. nice finish
description:
The Structure bookcase collection allows you to mix and match pieces and optional add-ins to fit your space and your needs. The tall, wide bookcase is ideal for small areas where multifunctional storage is required. With four shelves, the bookcase can stand alone in a tight space or join forces with other Structure pieces to form a solid storage area that can hold baskets, office supplies, or eclectic displays.

Set includes: One (1) bookshelfMaterials: PEFC certified sustainable wood Finish: Oak, whiteDimensions: 59.5 inches high x 31.5 inches wide x 13.8 inches deep StyleContemporaryMaterialWoodFinishOak Finish, White FinishShelf TypeBookshelvesAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorBrown, WhiteNumber of Shelf4
